editorial.name: Bathtime Fun
editorial.subtitle: We’ve selected 6 items to make bathtime fun.

item.name: Summer Infant Comfy Clean Deluxe Newborn to Toddler Tub, Teal

description.short: Designed for total comfort and support, the Summer Infant Comfy Clean Deluxe Newborn to Toddler Tub is sure to keep a smile on your little one’s face during bath time. This extra large tub includes a soft fabric sling that gently cradles your baby. As your little one grows, the foam pads and contoured sides and seating areas ensure baby stays safely (and comfortably) in place.
description.long:
Extra-large 3-stage tub grows with your baby.
  • Newborn fabric sling cradles baby, features a cushioned headrest, 
  • Padded recline backrest with side supports for comfort and support, 
  • Spacious toddler seating area

description.short:

  • These plush bath robes are fun and cozy after the bath!
description.long:

  • Super soft fabric is just like a blanket so baby is cozy and comfortable
  • Hood keeps baby warm and waist tie helps robe stay on
  • Fits babies up to 9 Months

item.name: Luvable Friends Baby Washcloths, Blue, 6 Pack

description.short: The Luvable Friends Washcloths are made from cotton rich terry that is absorbent and soft on your baby's gentle skin. Two feature cute octopus designs and four have solid colors, and they make getting squeaky clean easy and fun. They are ideal at bath time or whenever your little one needs to wash up. The toddler washcloths, 6 pack, octopus makes an ideal gift for you or for any parent to be for a baby shower. They are cute and soft against their skin and you can never have too many washcloths when it comes to bath time and washing your baby. They are super soft and thick enough while still being pliable.
description.long:
Luvable Friends Washcloths, 6 Pack, Octopus, Multiple Colors:
  • 6-pack washcloth set featuring 6 knitted terry washcloths
  • Adorable octopus designs
  • Made with 75% cotton and 25% polyester
  • Washcloths are 9" x 9"
  • Terry washcloths, multiple colors include blue, pink, and yellow

editorial.name: Crib
editorial.subtitle: We’ve chosen this crib because it’s a blank slate. It will match with any theme. Five stars, too!

item.name: Delta Children Canton 4-in-1 Convertible Crib Gray

description.short: Truly timeless, the Canton 4-in-1 Convertible Crib from Delta Children is embellished with a sleek, sleigh-style headboard, beautifully curved legs, and a versatile design that provides your little one a safe place to sleep, year after year! Built from strong and sturdy wood, this durable baby crib can accommodate all your child's sleeping needs — an adjustable mattress support with three positions allows you to easily lower the mattress as your baby grows, plus it converts to a toddler bed, daybed and full size bed with headboard when your child is ready to make the transition to a big kid bed. The Canton 4-in-1 Convertible Crib from Delta Children includes a Toddler Guardrail and Daybed Rail; Full Size Bed Rails sold separately. Available in multiple finishes. Delta Children was founded around the idea of making safe, high-quality cribs affordable for all families. That's why all Delta Children cribs are JPMA certified, and are tested to meet or exceed industry standards.
description.long:
Delta Children Canton 4-in-1 Convertible Crib, Grey:
  • Delta Children was founded around the idea of making safe, high-quality cribs affordable for all families — that's why all Delta Children cribs are JPMA certified, and are tested to meet or exceed industry standards
  • Converts to toddler bed, daybed and full size bed (Daybed Rail and Toddler Guardrail are included; Full Size Bed rails #0020 sold separately)
  • Coordinates with a variety of changing tables and dressers in matching finishes (sold seperately)
  • Assembled dimensions: 54.25"W x 35"D x 43.25"H
  • Expertly crafted by Delta Children and easy for you to assemble
  • Adjustable height mattress support with 3 convenient positions to grow with your baby
  • Uses a standard size crib mattress (sold separately)
  • JPMA certified to meet or exceed all safety standards set by the CPSC and ASTM
  • Tested for lead and other toxic elements to meet or exceed government and ASTM safety standards
  • Visit www.deltachildren.com for an assembly video for your crib
  • Model# 7888-026
  • Mattress sold separately. See our assortment of crib mattresses

item.name: Chicco NextFit iX Zip Convertible Car Seat, Eclipse

description.short:
The Chicco NextFit iX Zip Convertible Car Seat fits your vehicle and fits your child with proven SuperCinch LATCH functionality and a LockSure vehicle belt-tightening system, plus easy-to-use adjustability designed to comfortably accommodate growing children from 5 to 65 pounds. It also features a zip-off seat pad for machine washing.

The NextFit iX Zip features a 9-position ReclineSure leveling system and dual RideRight bubble level-indicators to help achieve and verify proper angle in the vehicle seat. For installation with LATCH, premium connectors and a SuperCinch tightener help achieve a secure fit with a fraction of the effort. (When it’s time to switch from rear-facing to forward-facing, the LATCH strap passes easily through the built-in slide path for proper repositioning.) For installation with the vehicle seat belt, a LockSure belt-tightening system makes it easy to position, tighten and lock the belt into place.

The NextFit iX Zip is engineered to last with built-in “fit-ability” for every stage, including a removable infant insert and smooth one-hand headrest adjustment with nine positions. As the headrest is raised, the shoulder strap position also raises and widens to accommodate growing children without re-threading. The harness also features an easy-pull, force-multiplying tightener and removable, machine-washable shoulder pads. For easier in/out, the NextFit iX Zip is equipped with a padded ComfortFlex harness management system that holds both sides of the waist belt out of the way until the child is ready to be buckled.

The NextFit iX Zip has a steel-reinforced frame and is lined with EPS energy-absorbing foam for superior side-impact protection.

For use from 5-40 lbs in Rear-Facing mode, from 22-65 lbs in Forward-Facing mode, and up to 49".
description.long:
• ReclineSure 9-position leveling system for an accurate fit in a wider range of vehicles
  • Dual RideRight bubble level-indicators verify seat angle in both rear-facing and forward-facing modes
  • Premium connectors and a SuperCinch tightener help achieve a secure installation with LATCH
  • LockSure belt-tightening system helps achieve a secure installation with vehicle seat belt
  • 9-position easy-adjust headrest and no-rethread harness accommodate growing children
  • Easy-pull, force-multiplying harness tightener for a secure child fit with less effort
  • Zip & Wash seat pad easily zips out from shell for machine washing
  • Padded ComfortFlex harness system keeps both sides of waist belt out of the way for easy in/out!
  • Removable infant insert accommodates infants from 5-11 lbs
  • Steel-reinforced frame with EPS energy-absorbing foam is side-impact tested for superior protection
